76. Code category entity and repository
In the Spring Boot application. Spring Data JPA is used to interact(tương tác) with database.
- Create table from code
- Entity or Repository bean are created and manage by JPA entities. So when start application.
We specify path(đường dẫn) to confirm package entity or repo by @EntityScan("package.entity") to management.